text: Clint Banbury (born 31 October 1949) is a Canadian equestrian. He competed in two events at the 1972 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1949 births Category:Living people Category:Canadian male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Canada Category:Equestrians at the 1972 Summer Olympics Category:Pan American Games medalists in equestrian Category:Pan American Games gold medalists for Canada Category:Pan American Games silver medalists for Canada Category:Equestrians at the 1971 Pan American Games Category:People from Wolseley, Saskatchewan Category:Sportspeople from Saskatchewan
